FBIS3-33710 "drnes020_n_94004" FBIS-NES-94-020 Document Type:Daily Report 31 Jan 1994 LEBANON Hizballah Confirms Holding 2 Israelis, Not Arad JN2801130794 Kuwait AL-WATAN in Arabic 23 Jan 94 p 24 JN2801130794 Kuwait AL-WATAN Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Dawud al-Mani dispatch from Damascus] [Excerpt] Hizballah's Deputy Secretary General 'Ammar al-Musawi denied having information that Israeli navigator Ron Arad, missing since 1986, is being held by Hizballah. He added: We have always and repeatedly said that Hizballah has nothing to do with Ron Arad. He confirmed that Hizballah is holding only two Israeli soldiers. [passage omitted]
